phpMyAdmin - Readme
===================

  A set of PHP-scripts to adminstrate MySQL over the WWW.

  Version 2.2.0rc3 - 22/07/2001
  -----------------------------
  http://phpwizard.net/projects/phpMyAdmin/
  http://phpmyadmin.sourceforge.net/

